1
00:00:10,600 --> 00:00:12,640
Why were you late, P’ Cir?

2
00:00:12,960 --> 00:00:13,960
I’m sorry.

3
00:00:17,080 --> 00:00:18,800
Who are you?
You’re not P’ Cir.

4
00:00:19,400 --> 00:00:20,480
