5
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:27,080
You’re the reason I want
to fight for the first time.

6
00:00:29,200 --> 00:00:30,280
Don’t you dare, Ai Phu.

7
00:00:30,840 --> 00:00:31,840
Keep in mind.

8
00:00:33,240 --> 00:00:34,400
You’re just the substitute.

9
00:00:36,400 --> 00:00:37,880
- Khun Sisira.
- Yes?

10
