16
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:40,440
Sawasdee krub.

17
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:45,120
Someone please tell me
what the hell day this is.

18
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,960
Why are random people
showing up out of nowhere?

19
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:41,480
EP VI: The Meaning of Family

20
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:45,320
Ai Cir, something’s been bugging me.

21
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:54,200
No.

22
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:07,240
Ai Cir, how long have
you and I been friends?

23
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:09,200
